At ACON labs, we are making a difference in medical care by offering medical devices for diagnosing a variety of conditions.
We are looking for a Scientist to join our team! With guidance and training, this person will research and develop product, conduct validation studies, data analysis and transfer the developed product to manufacture.
The essential duties/responsibilities for this position are:
Develop the new product research and development plans;
Plan and establish daily and weekly working schedule to meet project target timeline;
Write the study protocols and conduct product development, product validation and clinical evaluation;
Transfer the developed product to technical team at manufacture;

